  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "题目描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "给定正整数对 $(a, m)$，求乘法逆元 $a^{-1} \\bmod m$。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "数据不保证 $m$ 为质数，注意无解情况。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输入描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "第一行输入测试组数 $T\\ (1 \\le T \\le 10^4)$。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "接下来 $T$ 行，每行输入两个整数 $a, m\\ (1 \\le a < m \\le 10^9)$。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输出描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "对于每组测试用例，输出一行一个整数，表示表达式 $a^{-1} \\bmod m$ 的值。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>如果无解请输出 -1。</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "样例",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "输入",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "text",
              "code": "1\n2 3",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "输出",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "text",
              "code": "2",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "样例说明",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "无",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "利用扩展欧几里得算法求解整数 $x, y$ 使",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$a \\cdot x + m \\cdot y = \\gcd(a, m)$$",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "若 $\\gcd(a, m) = 1$，则上式化为 $a \\cdot x + m \\cdot y = 1$，两边对 $m$ 取模可得 $a \\cdot x \\equiv 1 \\pmod m$，因此 $x$ 对 $m$ 取非负最小剩余即可作为逆元：$x' = (x \\bmod m + m) \\bmod m$。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tll a, m; cin >> a >> m;\n\tll x0, y0;\n\tll g = Math::exgcd(a, m, x0, y0);\n\tif (g != 1) {\n\t\tcout << -1 << endl;\n\t\treturn;\n\t}\n\tll dx = m / g;\n\tll x = (x0 % dx + dx) % dx;\n\tcout << x << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
